        <profile name="Hive Mind Direction" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="d093-788e-d736-2f3d">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit Activates while it has Hive Minded, this unit gains the following ability until the next time it is Activated:


Terror Skirmishers: For each attack that targets this unit while it is the closest of your units to the attacking unit, the Hit Roll for that attack is worsened by 1.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Screaming Swarm" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="2ce9-d17b-9099-8355">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit&apos;s End step, if this turn was not your second turn in a row, take another turn.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
    </selectionEntry>
    <selectionEntry type="upgrade" import="true" name="Psychic Powers of the Zoanthropes (Reference)" hidden="false" id="5d67-6ad6-9a8b-0be4" sortIndex="-4">
      <constraints>
        <constraint type="max" value="1" field="selections" scope="force" shared="true" id="f4c7-ee89-2232-154c" includeChildSelections="false"/>
        <constraint type="min" value="1" field="selections" scope="force" shared="true" id="c26a-edab-3612-8b58" includeChildSelections="false"/>
        <constraint type="max" value="1" field="selections" scope="force" shared="true" id="452f-6463-c226-4602" includeChildSelections="false"/>
      </constraints>
      <categoryLinks>
        <categoryLink name="Configuration" hidden="false" id="49e1-7e19-2b09-e44d" targetId="9cd6-0442-3f35-6b52" primary="true"/>
      </categoryLinks>
      <profiles>
        <profile name="1 Hypnotic Gaze" typeId="6406-cf2b-ec5b-c7e6" typeName="Psychic Power" hidden="false" id="0d70-ad02-068b-0121">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4b9e-dc73-b312-b42d">Select a visible enemy unit within 24&quot;. Until the next time this unit is Activated or dies, the selected enemy unit cannot be selected for Activation unless their controlling player has no other units available for Activation. Then, this unit suffers 3 Suppression.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="2 Dominion" typeId="6406-cf2b-ec5b-c7e6" typeName="Psychic Power" hidden="false" id="8af4-fc5f-c530-11f1">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4b9e-dc73-b312-b42d">Select one of your other ready units within 12&quot; of this unit. After this unit&apos;s End step, you may take another turn. During that turn, for each attack the selected unit makes, add 2 to the Hit Roll for that attack. Then, this unit suffers 3 Suppression.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="3 Paroxysm" typeId="6406-cf2b-ec5b-c7e6" typeName="Psychic Power" hidden="false" id="ab1b-1929-f2fd-cd38">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4b9e-dc73-b312-b42d">For each single dice in this unit’s last Psychic Test, select a different enemy unit within 16&quot; of this unit. Then, each selected unit suffers X Suppression where X is equal to the result of that single dice. Then, this unit suffers 3 Suppression.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="4 Warp Lance" typeId="6406-cf2b-ec5b-c7e6" typeName="Psychic Power" hidden="false" id="bc0c-9582-3e98-99f6">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4b9e-dc73-b312-b42d">Select an enemy unit within 16” of and visible to this unit. The selected unit suffers X+2D3 SW where X is equal to the selected units Toughness. Then, this unit suffers Suppression equal to X.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="5 Warp Blast" typeId="6406-cf2b-ec5b-c7e6" typeName="Psychic Power" hidden="false" id="a523-aef4-bae3-069c">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4b9e-dc73-b312-b42d">Select an enemy unit with 16” and visible to this unit. That unit suffers 2+2D3 SW. Then, each unit within 6” of that unit suffers D3 SW.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="6 Hateful Will" typeId="6406-cf2b-ec5b-c7e6" typeName="Psychic Power" hidden="false" id="7ea2-0b70-f56e-6970">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4b9e-dc73-b312-b42d">Select an enemy unit within 16” and visible to this unit. The selected unit suffers 2D6+3 SW and this unit suffers X Suppression where X is equal to that roll.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
    </selectionEntry>
