          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">While this unit is in reserves, after an enemy unit without Fly finishes a March, roll a D6; if that unit advanced this turn, add 1 to the result. On a 5+, you may Deploy this unit within 4&quot; of that enemy unit and outside of the engagement range of enemy units.</characteristic>
